<task id="task-6174" class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">Set remote connection timeout for Git</title><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><context class="- topic/section task/context ">To set remote connection timeout for Git in <ph conkeyref="name-variables/ks-ped" class="- topic/ph "/>, do as follows:</context><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">From the main menu, go to <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Preferences</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Katalon</uicontrol> &gt; <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Git</uicontrol>.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image width="700" href="../image/ks-850-pe-git-preferences.png" class="- topic/image "/></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Enter the amount of time in second for remote connection timeout.</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Apply</uicontrol>.</cmd></step></steps></taskbody></task>